              "text": "Let's trade."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Where am I?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Logava",
              "text": "This is the marketplace of Hosidius. To the north west there's my sister's pub, and in the south is my grandfather's fruit farm. Do you need to buy anything while you're here?"
